    "id": "qa-purchase-loans-1",
    "source_id": "293",
    "question": "What is a Purchase Loans?",
    "answer": "Purchase Loans is a financing option designed for borrowers with that specific purchase or refinance goal. Loan terms and qualification details vary by lender, so side-by-side comparisons are important. You can learn more here: https://veecasa.com/purchase-loans/",
