  },
  {
    "id": "qa-purchase-loans-3",
    "source_id": "293",
    "question": "What are typical requirements for Purchase Loans?",
    "answer": "Typical requirements include acceptable credit, documented income or qualifying cash flow, manageable debt obligations, and property eligibility. Lender overlays can differ, so comparing lenders can improve approval odds. You can learn more here: https://veecasa.com/purchase-loans/",
